Reasoning: The paper discusses the design of a Grid resource information system using a Peer-to-Peer network model, which involves issues related to distributed computing, data structures, networking, databases, and network infrastructure. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). Other possible sub-categories include cs.Distributed (Distributed Systems), cs.DB (Databases), and cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture).
